  "title": "💥 Immediate Start! Sales Job with $3K–$6K/Month",
  "description": "<p><strong>Ready to launch a rewarding career in Sales &amp; Marketing?</strong><br>\nWe’re looking for driven individuals with a passion for people, learning, and growth to join our dynamic and expanding team. Whether you’re a fresh graduate, recently ORD-ed, or exploring a new career direction, this is your opportunity to gain hands-on experience, develop core business skills, and grow with one of the most vibrant teams in the industry.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔹 What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Represent Trusted Brands</strong> – Deliver engaging, face-to-face B2C presentations on behalf of reputable clients.</li>\n  <li><strong>Drive Customer Engagement</strong> – Learn to pitch, present, and promote products and services with confidence, professionalism, and integrity.</li>\n  <li><strong>Build Meaningful Connections</strong> – Develop relationships with clients and customers while expanding your personal and professional      network.</li>\n  <li><strong>Learn While You Earn</strong> – Receive comprehensive product training and ongoing mentorship from experienced team leaders.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔹 What We Offer</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Structured Career Growth</strong> – Clear and merit-based promotion pathways. Step into leadership roles based on your performance and potential.</li>\n  <li><strong>Supportive Team Culture</strong> – A collaborative environment where success is celebrated and teamwork is key.</li>\n  <li><strong>Travel Opportunities</strong> – Be part of high-energy campaigns locally and abroad.</li>\n  <li><strong>Performance Recognition</strong> – Incentives, rewards, and recognition for top performers.</li>\n  <li><strong>Continuous Learning</strong> – Access to regular workshops, coaching, and on-the-job development to fast-track your skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔹 Who We’re Looking For</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Energetic, outgoing individuals with a positive attitude</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills and a people-first mindset</li>\n  <li>Eager to learn, grow, and take on challenges</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates and ORD personnel are encouraged to apply</li>\n  <li>No prior experience required—just bring your enthusiasm and willingness to learn!</li>\n  <li><br></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ready to make your mark?</strong><br>\nJoin a company where your potential is recognized, and your growth is accelerated. Apply now and start building a career you’re proud of.</p>",
